{"word":"G1506 - εἰλικρινής - eilikrinḗs - i-lik-ree-nace' - Pure","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἰλικρινής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eilikrinḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">i-lik-ree-nace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Pure</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"துப்புரவான, உண்மையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"pure, unsullied, sincere"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;</b> <b>heile&#x0304;</b> (the sun&rsquo;s <i>ray</i>) and <a href=\"#/G2919 - κρίνω - krínō - kree'-no/2919\">G2919</a>; <i>judged by sunlight</i>, that is, tested as <i>genuine</i> (figuratively): - pure, sincere.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1505/1505\">G1505</a>, <a href=\"#/G1506/1506\">G1506</a>"}]}